        <item>
            <title>中国景区流行智能外骨骼租借，行山都可出「外挂」更加轻松</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/ai-helps-hiking/life-tech/%e6%88%80%e4%b8%8a%e5%b1%b1/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-helps-hiking</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/ai-helps-hiking/life-tech/%e6%88%80%e4%b8%8a%e5%b1%b1/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 11:27:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[恋上山]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[行山]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303602</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>中国多个旅游景区近日推出智能外骨骼装置租借服务，协助游客减轻登山体力负担。该设备由电力驱动，重量仅约 1.8 公斤，透过人工智能调节步伐，最高可降低 30% 体能消耗。现时深圳野生动物园、泰山及卢山等景区已提供服务，预计 2025 年内扩展至全国 25 个山岳型景区。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303738" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303739" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-1-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-1-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-1.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h01.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303740" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h01-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h01-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h01.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></a></p><h2>智能外骨骼提升登山体验</h2><p>智能外骨骼装置由腰部控制器及腿部支架组成，根据人体工学设计，搭载多模态感知系统，能识别行走及上下楼梯等动作，适时提供助力。续航达 3 至 5 小时，单次充电可行走约 14 公里。泰山文旅集团总经理王厚哲表示，外骨骼经深度学习可自动适应用家步伐，特别适合长者及体力较弱人士。有游客接受访问时表示，本来脚仍有点痛，使用后完全没感觉了；另外亦有游客指，外骨骼可自动抬腿，有种飘起来的感觉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250326005172-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250326005172-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250326005172.jpg 1019w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20250326005171-260409?chdtv">中时新闻报</a></p><h2>景区科技化趋势明显</h2><p>除外骨骼装置外，中国景区正积极引入其他智能装置，如机械狗运送物资、导游机械人及无人机外卖服务，提升游客体验。根据深圳市肯綮科技有限公司数据，全国逾 100 个景区有意引入外骨骼设备，数十个景区已进入测试阶段。深圳野生动物园企划部经理助理刘辉透露，免费试用一个多月已吸引数百人体验。</p><h2>价格与普及前景</h2><p>租借费用方面，泰山景区外骨骼装置定价为每 3 小时 80 元人民币（约港币 88 元），视乎使用地点或有折扣。肯綮科技产品总监杨工透露，智能外骨骼已量产，售价控制在 1 万人民币（约港币 1.1 万元）以内，未来有望进入个人市场，特别惠及行动不便人士。市场分析指，随着技术成熟及成本降低，外骨骼设备或于 3 至 5 年内普及至更多旅游及医疗场景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/043screenshot-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/043screenshot-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/043screenshot-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可以调校不同力度，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhcVykxaalM&amp;ab_channel=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E7%A4%BE">中国新闻社@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/046screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/046screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/046screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最高可降低 30% 体能消耗，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhcVykxaalM&amp;ab_channel=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E7%A4%BE">中国新闻社@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/018screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/018screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/018screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhcVykxaalM&amp;ab_channel=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E7%A4%BE">中国新闻社@YouTube</a></p><h2></h2><h2>总结与未来展望</h2><p>智能外骨骼租借服务为中国景区旅游注入科技元素，大幅提升长者及体弱游客的登山体验。随着装置量产及应用范围扩大，预计 2025 年将有更多景区加入，推动智慧旅游发展。惟成本与技术稳定性仍是普及关键，未来新闻或聚焦设备普及进度及用户反馈。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=600584">now</a>、<a href="https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20250326005171-260409?chdtv">中时新闻报</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/ai-helps-hiking/life-tech/%e6%88%80%e4%b8%8a%e5%b1%b1/">中国景区流行智能外骨骼租借，行山都可出「外挂」更加轻松</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
